## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible leadership styles or their nuanced impacts in different organizational contexts. Additionally, the effectiveness of a leadership style can vary significantly depending on the specific industry, organizational culture, and individual employee characteristics. Further empirical research could provide more comprehensive insights.

